{"type": "article", "id": 20832, "title": "混凝土袖扣", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-18T07:35:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607115458EScLPUBQOalgVFoW.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t印度一家设计工作室 Material Immaterial studio 曾经用方形的混凝土设计建筑模块，他们最近用混凝土做了一系列袖扣，有方形或圆形，一共 9 种。可以看到里面带有凹凸感的图形，组成楼梯、圆拱门、屋顶等不同的建筑元素，有混凝土本身的质感，但显得精致而有趣。每对售价 65 美元，<a href=\"http://www.tadpolestore.com/material-immaterial-studio\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150621yGT0AchjZ2FtSadQ.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150622kZzvsra5nuKd2lEM.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150622spA9DC6VvfdaMgHj.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150623ypjzKkRUt24X5V7B.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150623NQusxUoBwW8G1aTg.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150623LU5sTDEnjt2Zcv4r.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}